programme.sub-title: Si no lo veo no lo creo
programme.desc: Un delincuente trata de culpar por sus acciones a su familia. Un padre no tiene otra opción que entregar a su hijo a la policía. Los oficiales descubren cosas interesantes cuando buscan el auto de un padre de familia.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un oficial pide refuerzos cuando se ve en desventaja. Un hombre recibe más de lo que esperaba cuando trata de ayudar a su vecino. Esposos se separan después de que los agentes registran su vehículo.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre muy hábil hace todo lo posible para evadir a la policía. Personas nobles ponen sus vidas en riesgo cuando descubren un crimen violento. Una mujer es atrapada cometiendo el delíto, pero trata de negociar con los oficiales.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.sub-title: Entre la espada y la pared
programme.desc: Una persecución de autos de gran velocidad cambia de rumbo cuando el conductor huye a pie. Los ánimos entre los vecinos se encienden después de que los niños se practican ejercicio . Un conductor que se encuentra muy nervioso se enfurece después de que la policía registra a su pasajero.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un delincuente que se escapa de la cárcel busca refugio donde su abuela. Una explosión del pasado permite que los oficiales saquen un dispositivo de seguridad de los años 80. Más tarde, los vecinos preocupados se niegan a devolver un perro a sus dueños.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.sub-title: Arma de frente, rifle en la parte trasera
programme.desc: Los oficiales responden a un fatal accidente automovilístico. La policía interroga a un sospechoso por presunto robo, pero este asegura ser la verdadera víctima. Los oficiales encuentran a un hombre que dice padecer de un trastorno que lo obliga a escapar.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un preso en libertad condicional lleva a los oficiales a un callejón sin salida. Un novio celoso le cuenta a la policía su versión de los hechos, pero no puede ceñirse a su historia. Un oficial ayuda a algunas personas disgustadas a hacer las paces.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un detective se lesiona mientras persigue a un presunto ladrón de coches. Una pareja queda atrapada es esposada después de una pelea en un bar. Los oficiales encuentran una sorprendente variedad de objetos en el vehículo de un sospechoso.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre tiene un episodio de taquicardia por lo que requiere asistencia médica. Un sujeto que infringe la ley no parece comprender la gravedad de su situación. Cuando la policía cuestiona a un trío bastante interesante, parecen estar dos contra uno.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre confiesa que de no ser por su novia se habría salido con la suya. Acuden a los agentes cuando la búsqueda de trabajo de una madre se vuelva más compleja aún. Los oficiales se enfrentan a un hombre un poco nervioso y que al parecer tiene malos hábitos.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un joven recibe un llamado de atención cuando los oficiales lo encuentran infringiendo la ley. En un retén policial es detenido un trío que al parecer tienen mucho que ocultar. Los oficiales juegan a arreglar una pelea familiar, para que una familia haga las paces luego de una pelea que desató un juego de mesa.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso huye desesperadamente de los policías después de escuchar varios disparos. Un padre y una hija se encuentran atemorizados a causa de un hombre que empuña un destornillador. La policía atrapa varias de mujeres atractivas, aparentemente, tomando malas decisiones.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un conductor bastante desafiante con la ley, no lo puede creer cuando su madre no se pone de su lado. Los oficiales descubren a un hombre con un peculiar disfraz durante una parada de tráfico. Los oficiales protegen a una madre que trabaja arduament, pues esta recibiendo visitas repentinas.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un conductor con evasivas, les afirma a los policias que es víctima de una chica muy mala. Una mujer en estado de embarazo toma algunas decisiones algo cuestionables. Un sospechoso de robo encuentra paz confesando sus acciones.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre enfurecido le cuesta aceptar la verdad. Los oficiales cuestionan a un grupo de personas resevadas,esforzandosen por confirmar sus sospechas. Los niños llaman a la policía, pues una discusión entre sus padres se torna muy violenta.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Los oficiales vienen al rescate cuando un hombre con problemas ha tocado fondo. Los policías son llamados cuando un hombre comienza una guerra de comida. Los agentes capturan a un hombre desprevenido mientras esta en busca de un estacionamiento.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre que esta siendo buscado, se queja de dolor en el pecho después de que golpea a otro conductor. Una mujer se enoja y llama a la policía a causa de una bolsa de papas picante. Un hombre violento finalmente aprende donde su novia tiene un limite.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Supuestos ladrones de joyas intentan escapar de la policia, durante una persecución a alta velocidad. El arresto de un hombre pelionero es un desafío. Una parada de tráfico lleva a una pelea de esposos, después de revelar algunos artículos ilegales.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un fugitivo desesperadamente decide huir a pie. Una novia sobreprotectora duda de la policía y la esposan. Un celoso pierde a la novia y más después de buscar pleito con el hijo.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre de delito reincidente lleva a la policía por un camino rugoso. Un oficial aconseja a dos adolescentes en un auto estacionado. Unos oficiales le cuentan el secreto a una mujer de su hermano.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: La policía busca a un sospechoso en un barrio y lo encuentran en un aprieto. Se investiga a un auto estacionado detrás de una iglesia. Un oficial aconseja a una madre joven con un pasado problemático.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Una persecución a pie termina con el sospechoso en una situación vergonzosa. Un automovilista llama a la policía cuando un peatón pierde la calma. Un hombre arriesga su relación con malas manías.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un conductor se enoja cuando se le interroga. Durante una persecución a coche un hombre le habla a su esposa y la policía se sorprende. Un mentiroso es atrapado y se le da una prueba de inocencia.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Con la policía en los talones, el mundo se le cierra a un sospechoso. Una mujer llorando por su esposo violento llama a la policía. Durante un retén alguien intenta escapar de la policía y su pasado.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso crea un enorme problema cuando decide huir. Una mujer confiesa sus fallas arriesgando su matrimonio. Los agentes investigan a una sospechosa, pero la amiga termina detenida.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Rodeado de oficiales, un pasajero se arriesga. Se enojan dos compañeras cuando una le da de comer huevos a su perro. Un oficial actúa rápido al ver un objeto peligroso en el asiento de un vehículo.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un preso en libertad condicional escapa de la policía, pero se le acaba la suerte. Una pareja alega y los vecinos hablan a la policía. Un hombre desorientado tiene un accidente raro y culpa al clima.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Una pistola taser se descarga en un sospechoso errático. Un delincuente intenta convencer a los detectives de que no lo vieron cometer ningún crimen. Un oficial supervisa una transacción absurda.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un principiante lamenta su delito y decisiones destructivas. Un conductor no creíble le dice a la policía que es víctima de un crimen. Un oficial anima a una chica con problemas a cambiar su vida.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.sub-title: Siesta en el espacio de rastreo
programme.desc: Un sospechoso huyente inventa excusas para evitar la cárcel. Un conductor durmiéndose pide que la policía no le diga a su esposa. Una llamada de allanamiento causa un tormento en un vecindario.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un delincuente corre cuando oficiales lo ven en un lugar prohibido. Dos jóvenes se tardan en detener a un ladrón de bicicletas y llaman a la policía. Un problema domestico se complica malignamente.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre rebelde intenta despistar a los oficiales. Un conductor bien vestido quiebra barricadas. Los oficiales se sorprenden cuando una llamada doméstica da un giro inesperado.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Viendo una buena oportunidad un sospechoso va a las carreras. Se atrapa a un hombre con objetos desagradables. Se atrapa a un hombre en una operación encubierta, aun así, no admite su crimen.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: La policía intenta atrapar a un sospechoso por robo de vehículo armado. La policía llega a una escena caótica y un testigo aclara las cosas. Un ciclista rezongón culpa su forma de ser en animé.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Alguien con un corazón roto maneja peligrosamente. Se atrapa a un miembro de la Asociación de padres y maestros dando un mal ejemplo. Seguir adelante es difícil para una mujer con un pasado malo.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Es como una reunión cuando la policía alcanza a alguien que reconoce. La amante de un hombre hace problemas con la esposa. Los oficiales batallan con dos sospechosos que no dan respuestas concretas.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre buscado huye y la policía va muy cerca detrás de él. La policía persigue a una persona manejando nerviosamente. Un retén arriesga a un auto lleno de gente que tiene mucho que ocultar.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Los oficiales se ven obligados a usar guantes cuando detienen a un sospechoso asustado con una condición grave de la piel. Un futuro papá trata de correr. Un rapero empieza a cantar cuando lo esposan.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Se somete a un hombre que está convencido que un animal salvaje lo sigue. Un cumpleaños se descontrola rápidamente cuando se involucran las armas. La policía ayuda con un problema domestico volátil.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un barrio tranquilo se interrumpe. Un hombre desafortunado trata de ocultar su culpabilidad al tirar unas prendas. Hay puñetazos cuando un dueño de tienda enfrenta a alguien que le robó.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: La policía encuentra más que golosinas en el bolsillo de un sospechoso. Un conductor armado da un relato no creíble para justificar su arma. Una discusión termina con una llamada a Control Animal.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre llama a la policía cuando ve un robo en la licorería. Un conductor pierde a su amiga cuando le roba su camioneta. Los oficiales le sugieren a un joven que sea mejor ejemplo para su hermano.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: La policía evita un allanamiento posiblemente mortal en una casa. Un pasajero tenso empieza a rezongar antes de que los oficiales digan una palabra. La policía busca la bicicleta robada de un joven.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Los oficiales persiguen a un ciclista casi desnudo por todo el vecindario. Un sospechoso hace una serie de movimientos equivocados frente a su novia. La policía encuentra a una mujer en un armario.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un conductor quiere regresar a casa para un cumpleaños. Un hombre teme confesar por qué sus huellas están en un arma. Un viaje para comprar comida de perro se convierte en un encuentro con la policía.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un conductor atrevido causa una persecución loca. Un pollero tiene una explicación poco clara de los objetos descubiertos en su carro. Un hombre impulsivo no reconocer sus errores fácilmente.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso que conduce ebrio dice que sólo salió a comprar un bocadillo. Una pareja se delata cuando la policía hace preguntas. La policía detiene a alguien que cree que se le tendió una trampa.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre intenta pelear con todo el vecindario. Un fugitivo está convencido de que la policía le dijo que se fuera en su bicicleta. Una mamá joven con problemas tiene una segunda oportunidad.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un motociclista causa una persecución por las calles. Ni un carro que no prende impide que un hombre corra de la policía. Un conductor no logra evadir a la policía y se disculpa raramente con su novia.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Durante una parada de tránsito un sospechoso decide huir a campo través. Una mujer rehúsa mentir por el amigo de su hijo. Se captura en video a un hombre escondiendo artículos en un lugar obvio.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: El último esfuerzo para huir de la policía termina en llamas. Varias unidades se unen para acabar con una situación peligrosa. La policía vigila una batalla de custodia conllevando comestibles caros.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Unas placas raras ayudan a prevenir un robo. Una pelea por un amor no correspondido se vuelve violenta. Se asombra la policía por la falta de ropa de un presunto incendiario.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Se desmiente a un sospechoso cuando su víctima presenta video de seguridad. El miedo le gana a un conductor cuando trata de escapar descuidadamente. Un viaje de noche al mercado termina en llanto.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Una pelea entre hermanos intensifica cuando uno saca un arma. Un hombre no mantiene distancia de su exnovia aunque es orden de juez. Los oficiales animan a una mujer que quiere control sobre su vida.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Los agentes capturar a un sospechoso y le salvan la vida. Un esposo reacciona mal cuando su esposa descubre sus actividades en internet. Un hombre agresivo enemista lastima a todos a su alrededor.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso prolonga su arresto negociando. El caos sigue cuando el gerente del club nocturno se enfrenta al empleado que robó su dinero. Un hombre insiste que quería ser arrestado.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Una noche en familia de ver fútbol resulta en pelea. Un ladrón conocido acaba con la buena voluntad de la policía al encontrarlo con bienes robados. Un experto de las calles admite no poder escapar.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso habitual no logra convencer a los oficiales que tenía buen motivo al correr. Un compañero entrometido impide que una pareja deje sus malos hábitos. Un esposo y esposa pelean por su bebé.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Una mujer moribunda intenta reconciliarse con su severo padre para que su hija ilegítima pueda vivir en un lugar seguro.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: La guía de Jonathan ayuda en una conexión amorosa entre Diana, la prima de Mark, y Scotty, un divertido e interesante abogado con tetraplejía.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan decide hacer un cambio de papeles entre un hombre millonario, despiadado y soberbio y un mendigo amable al que le queda poco tiempo de vida.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark le dan una lección a Laurie, una joven actriz cuya fama la está convirtiendo en una mala persona, afectando a su familia y robándole su infancia.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan debe juntar los vecinos de Helen para unirse y ayudar a salvar sus casas de unos desarrolladores corporativos que quieren desalojarlos.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: La hija de un entrenador de caballos y el hijo de un ranchero se conocen en un entrenamiento y nace una atracción entre ellos. Jonathan y Mark tienen que actuar de cupido para unirlos, a pesar de que él ya está comprometido.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Garth y Lizzy se fugan juntos y se casan. Ella descubre que tiene cáncer pero no quiere contárselo a Garth hasta no saber sus posibilidades de sobrevivir.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: La adicción a la cocaína de un presentador de TV (Robert Culp) incita a su preocupado hijo para entregarlo a la policía.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Los padres (Anne Jackson, Eli Wallach) de un niño en estado de coma tratan de consolar a su hija, que se siente responsable.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Un joven hombre imprudente (estrella invitada Pat O'Bryan) y una adolescente embarazada y soltera (estrella invitada Lori Griffin) aprenden una lección sobre el amor y la responsabilidad.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark (Michael Landon, Victor French) ayudan a una escritora solitaria (estrella invitada Didi Conn) a conocer un agente secreto (estrella invitada Warwick Sims) asesinado en 1968.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Negocios sucios de un empresario consiguen "matarlo", pero Jonathan y Mark arreglan una segunda oportunidad en la vida para él.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan Smith ayuda a los ancianos de un asilo a recuperar su vitalidad, al ofrecer gratis sus servicios de jardinería. Además, dos hermanos, uno de ellos alcohólico, también requieren de la gentileza de Jonathan.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Mark duda de Jonathan y es hostil con él. Por ese motivo, Jonathan decide revelarle a Mark su condición de ángel. Los ancianos se sienten destrozados por la noticia de la posible venta del asilo.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan acude al llamado de una madre que está afligida por la enfermedad terminal de su pequeño hijo Aitor, cuyo anhelo es tocar la luna. Además, Mark se topa con un niño problemático y trata de darle una segunda oportunidad.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark buscan trabajo como entrenadores de boxeo para poder ayudar a jóvenes llenos de ira. Mientras tanto, reaparece Morton Clay, también conocido como "el jinete enmascarado", acompañado de sus amigos.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan se encuentra con Sara, una joven cantante que desea saber más sobre su madre muerta, pero a su padre no le gusta hablar de ella. Sin embargo, la vida de Sara puede cambiar cuando un secreto sale a la luz.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Un atleta llamado Dick queda postrado en una silla de ruedas luego de un terrible accidente. El joven necesita la ayuda de Mark y Jonathan, pero también de Eleanor.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Un atleta llamado Dick queda postrado en una silla de ruedas luego de un terrible accidente. El joven necesita la ayuda de Mark y Jonathan, pero también de Eleanor.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Un anciano excéntrico que dice ser el Rey Arturo y su codicioso hijo reciben la ayuda de Jonathan y Mark. Además, asisten a una mujer que va a perder sus tierras por culpa del ambicioso heredero.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Un famoso actor contrata a Jonathan y a Mark para que cuiden a sus dos hijos. Sin embargo, los niños sienten mucho la ausencia de su padre.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.sub-title: Se solicita ayuda de un ángel
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark acuden al llamado de un par de ancianos que buscan la ayuda de un ángel para poder hacer una película que llegue al corazón de muchas personas.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Un hombre que estuvo en Vietnam descubre que tiene una hija llamada Nu Yen, que decide irse a vivir a Estados Unidos con él y su familia. Su hijo Brad es la única persona que no está feliz con esta situación, y Jonathan y Mark lo ayudan.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Mark y Jonathan ayudan a Barry, un heredero que debe hacerse cargo del hotel de su padre. Al mismo tiempo, debe decidir entre dos mujeres que lo desean: una antigua compañera de clase, y una mujer que trabaja en el hotel.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: La expansión de un negocio de autos amenaza a un orfanato justo en plena Navidad. Jonathan y Mark deben hacer comprender al dueño del negocio cuál es el significado de estas fiestas para que no lleve a cabo sus planes.

programme.title: El Crepusculo De Un Dios
programme.desc: Sonia conoce roberto, una actor desahuciado y con pocos dias de vida. ambos se enamoran. poco despues un policia llega buscando a sonia, pero este es interceptado por una condesa, quien lo distrae y con quien pasa el ano nuevo jugando poquer, situacion que roberto y sonia aprovechan para huir. sin embargo, al subir a la avioneta en la que escaparan roberto sufre un infarto. sonia es capturada y condenada a morir en la silla electrica por asesinato, pero conserva la alegria de reunirse con roberto en el mas alla.

programme.title: El Gran Relajo Mexicano
programme.desc: CANDIDO LLEGA A LA CAPITAL CON SU MUJER PETRONILA Y SU HIJA INOCENCIA. UN PAISANO LOS HOSPEDA TEMPORALMENTE, ELLOS SE HACEN VENDEDORES AMBULANTES PERO LIDERES E INSPECTORES ACABAN CON SU MERCANCIA. SOCRATES, UN TIPO QUE FINGE SER ATROPELLADO PARA PEDIR DINERO, LOS HOSPEDA Y LOS HACE MUSICOS CALLEJEROS. UN DIA TOCAN PARA UN MINISTRO Y LO SALVAN DE UN ATENTADO. EL EN AGRADECIMIENTO LES DA TRABAJO Y CARLOS, EL HIJO DEL MINISTRO SE ENAMORA DE INOCENCIA. UNOS TIPOS INTENTAN SOBORNAR AL MINISTRO Y A SU HIJO PERO ELLOS LO RECHAZAN. EL MINISTRO RECOMIENDA A CANDIDO COMO ARCHIVISTA. LOS CORRUPTOS AMENAZAN A LA FAMILIA DEL MINISTRO, QUE FLAQUEA Y SU HIJO SE VA ENOJADO A CASA DE SOCRATES. ALLI EL MINISTRO PREPARA UNA TRAMPA A LOS CORRUPTOS. CANDIDO E INOCENCIA LO AYUDAN Y ATRAPAN A LOS DELINCUENTES CON EL DINERO DEL SOBORNO. CARLOS E INOCENCIA SE CASAN Y VAN AL RANCHO DE CANDIDO, A QUIEN EL MINISTRO REGALA UN TRACTOR.

programme.title: Pension De Artistas
programme.desc: Despues de una fallida gira artistica, tongolele, maria victoria y lola beltran, terminan huyendo de la ultima presentacion a la pension de artistas, acompanadas por su agente tilin. el problema se agudiza cuando se enteran que la hipoteca de esa casa esta a punto de vencer, por lo que deben ayudar a la casera prudencia, mas tarde rafael, un cantante que se hace pasar por medico, les propone formar un espectaculo de revista a traves de gustavo, amigo de tilin, asi que deben encontrar la forma de obtener el patrocinio, aunque para ello deban de valerse de una gran mentira. una vez logrado el montaje con su maestro pedro vargas, las artistas se enfrentan a su prueba de fuego, la aceptacion del publico o el fracaso y la deuda.

programme.title: El Marido De Mi Novia
programme.desc: RAQUEL DEBE ROBAR PARA SOSTENER A SU MARIDO LISIADO, EL CUAL QUEDO CONFINADO A UNA SILLA DE RUEDAS POR UN ACCIDENTE DONDE MURIO SU PEQUENA HIJA. EN ESTE AMBIENTE CONOCE A PACO, QUIEN DESARROLLA LA MISMA ACTIVIDAD Y DECIDEN ASOCIARSE. JUNTOS VIVEN UNA SERIE DE AVENTURAS QUE LOS LLEVA INCLUSO A TENER UNA TERCERA SOCIA. PACO SE ENAMORA DE RAQUEL, AL IGUAL QUE EL NEUROLOGO QUE HA SIDO CONTRATADO PARA DAR TRATAMIENTO AL MARIDO DISCAPACITADO. RAQUEL ACOMPANADA DE PACO LLEGA SORPRESIVAMENTE A VER A SU MARIDO PARA DARLE LA BUENA NOTICIA DE QUE SE PUEDE CURAR CON UNA OPERACION Y DESCUBRE A SU ESPOSO CAMINANDO. LLENO DE CORAJE, PACO LO MATA POR LO QUE ES LLEVADO A LA CARCEL Y RAQUEL Y EL MEDICO TERMINAN CASANDOSE.

programme.title: Rostro Infernal
programme.desc: El conde brankovan posee la formula de la inmortalidad robada a paracelso hace mas de cuatrocientos anos; pero para seguir viviendo debe chupar el cerebro de seres humanos, y como tiene rostro deforme usa una mascara y lo ayudan los cuerpos sin voluntad de los cientificos a los que descerebra. es amante de la vedette viki y secuestra a un pianista. el inspector portillo investiga las desapariciones y sigue a brankovan hasta la casa del profesor robert, donde el monstruo, ya con mascara, pasa por un colega. ya en su laboratorio bebe el cerebro del pianista y de una investigadora. la vedette se pone celosa por otra mujer y brankovan estrangula a una cantante que lo ama al confundirla con ella. la vedette lo delata a la policia y sus trabajadores se golpean solos confundidos con la luz del cabaret. brankovan se electrocuta en su laboratorio al ser sorprendido por la policia.

programme.title: Caceria Humana
programme.desc: Dos adolescentes alberto y su novia lucy se escapan a la playa, el problema es que el padre de ella se opone a esta relacion por sus diferencias economicas, asi que los manda a buscar en su luna de miel, a la par, un hombre persigue a la pareja provocandoles un accidente automovilistico que les quita la vida. mas tarde, rodrigo, hermano de alberto, acude a identificar su cuerpo, alli se entera que no es el primer incidente que le ocurre a otras parejas, ademas, el mismo es victima de un atentado, situacion que le hace sospechar mas cuando conoce a olivia, una mujer que tambien perdio a su hermano en las mismas circunstancias, de este modo, ambos intentan descubrir la verdad detras de sus muertes pero a alberto le aguarda una terrible sorpresa.

programme.title: Juego Peligroso
programme.desc: Dos historias que tienen como fondo la bahia de rio de janeiro, brasil. en ho, leonardo, un publicista, halla en la carretera a claudia y luis, unos recien casados cuyo auto se descompuso. su acto de buen samaritano da pie a una relacion extra-marital con claudia y a un chantaje. divertimento: cuenta la historia de lena y mario, una pareja de amantes cuyo empeno por enganarse mutuamente culmina en una cadena de asesinatos y en el descubrimiento del erotismo ligado a la muerte por parte de lena.

programme.title: Kermesse
programme.desc: En rio verde esta proxima la kermesse del pueblo con motivo de festejar al santo patron, pero blanca quien esta contratada para amenizar la kermesse sufre un retraso en la carretera, por lo que alberto quien pasaba por ahi le da un aventon. al llegar a rio verde blanca y alberto por asares del destino conocen al amor de su vida y cada uno lucha por conseguir su felicidad ya que se fijan en la persona equivocada.

programme.title: El Picaro
programme.desc: Fortunato es muy torpe y esta enamorado de anita. cuando se entera de que un futbolista la pretende, lo manda a golpear. asi, resulta sustituido en un partido y su equipo casi alcanza la victoria.

programme.title: Jefe Policiaco
programme.desc: SE CUENTA LA HISTORIA DE LA RIVALIDAD ENTRE DOS HOMBRE QUE SURGIO DESDE SU JUVENTUD, CUANDO SE JUGABAN EL AMOR DE LA MUJER MAS BELLA DE LA REGION, ACRECENTANDOSE CADA DIA. AHORA SON DOS POLICIAS, DOS JEFES AL MANDO, QUE PODRAN CONTROLAR TODO MENOS EL ODIO ENTRE ELLOS.

programme.title: El Nino Y La Estrella
programme.desc: UN NINO AYUDA A SU ABUELO EN LA CAPTURA DE PAJAROS PARA VENDERLOS EN EL PUEBLO, NO OBSTANTE SU VIDA CAMBIA CUANDO SU ABUELO ES DETENIDO Y ACUSADO INJUSTAMENTE POR EL CARGO DE ROBO, ESTO TRAE CONSECUENCIAS GRAVES PARA AMBOS, PUES EL PEQUENO ES OBLIGADO A IR A UN ORFANATO, PESE A ESTA SITUACION, SU ABUELO LOGRA CONTACTARLO Y LE PIDE QUE DEJE EN LIBERTAD A LOS PAJAROS PERO MIENTRAS TANTO DEBE ENFRENTAR UNA NUEVA VIDA CON SUS EN ESTA DIFICIL PRUEBA.

programme.title: Misericordia
programme.desc: Bedigna es una mujer ya adulta que junto con un grupo de limosneros asiste a las afueras de la iglesia de san sebastian para juntar un poco de dinero. benigna con el dinero que logra reunir ayuda a gente mas necesitada que ella, como lo es yuco quien esta ciega, a una senora dona francisca que le ayuda a la limpieza de su casa. pronto bedigna y dona francisca obtienen la ayuda economica de un viejo amigo don carlos quien esta dispuesta a ayudarlas con la condicion de que sigan sus consejos como el ahorrar y apuntar en una libreta todos sus ingresos. pero benigna a pesar de esta ayuda no termina de pedir limosna para ayudar a las personas mas necesitadas.

programme.title: RESCATE
programme.desc: Debora Lopez es una policia con una fe inquebrantable y una vocacion sin limites para proteger y servir. Su vida toma un giro inesperado cuando participa en una operacion que termina en tragedia. Ahora, peleara por su creencia en un mejor servicio policial mas humano.

programme.title: LAS CARAS DEL DIABLO 1
programme.desc: Pedro Ramirez es un joven detective obsesionado con el asesinato de un menor. Tres anos despues del crimen, su hija Sarah es secuestrada en circunstancias muy similares, comenzando una persecucion imparable para capturar al criminal.

programme.title: EL ULTIMO MINUTO
programme.desc: Cuando Karla descubre que se esta muriendo, decide volver a conectarse con Angie, una sobrina que no habia conocido en anos. La nina esta siendo tratada despues de un suicidio fallido, por lo que Karla decide llevarla a su casa, sin saber si podria manejar los ataques de panico y depresion de Angie, y su propia mortalidad.

programme.title: EL ULTIMO MINUTO
programme.desc: Cuando Karla descubre que se esta muriendo, decide volver a conectarse con Angie, una sobrina que no habia conocido en anos. programme.title: UN AMOR DE PELICULA
programme.desc: Bernardo es un productor de cine cercano a la bancarrota que decide convencer erroneamente a un famoso director de cine de hacer una mala pelicula para poder ganar mucho dinero. Laura, su novia y agente, se convierte en su confidente y musa.

programme.title: AZOTES DE BARRIO
programme.desc: Luego de cumplir una condena de siete anos en prision, Donay busca dejar atras su pasado criminal. Sin embargo, conoce a una mujer que aun esta en prision y se enamora de ella.

Leo esta en crisis con su pareja. Trabaja doce horas por dia como chofer de taxi en Rosario. La ciudad esta cambiando, y eso lo agobia. Un suceso imprevisto en su taxi lo obliga a modificar su rutina. En las calles de la tensa ciudad se cruza con situaciones que agudizan su malestar. siempre ha contenido, ahora parece a punto de explotar.

programme.title: NO HAY REMEDIO
programme.desc: Roberto, Fonso y Angel son tres viejos llenos de remordimientos y suenos no cumplidos. Deciden robar una farmacia como una forma facil de alcanzar esas necesidades insatisfechas antes de que sea demasiado tarde. Pero lo que parece ser un trabajo facil se convierte en un camino inesperado hacia una vida completa.

programme.title: HIJOS NUESTROS
programme.desc: A veces los vinculos se pueden construir a partir de las pasiones. A veces esos vinculos se pueden convertir en pasiones. Un taxista porteno fanatico de San Lorenzo se cruza con una madre soltera y su hijo.

programme.title: EL VERANO QUE TE VIMOS
programme.desc: Luego de un tiempo sin verse, un grupo de amigos se reencuentra para festejar ano nuevo en las sierras cordobesas. Durante esos dias resurgiran tensiones del pasado y conflictos que tarde o temprano deberan ser enfrentados.

programme.title: EL PEOR COMEDIANTE
programme.desc: Aurelio es un comediante con mala conducta cuya indisciplina acabo con su carrera. Abandonado por su mujer y olvidado por el publico, su unico amigo es su manager de toda la vida, Antonio. Juntos planean superar la depresion y preparan su regreso triunfal a los escenarios.

programme.title: 27 DEMASIADO PRONTO
programme.desc: Documental centrado en aquellos musicos que se fueron demasiado pronto, a la edad temprana de 27 anos. A pesar de que entre 1969 y 1971 fueron varios los artistas que murieron a esa edad (Brian Jones, Jimi Hendrix, Janis Joplin y Jim Morrison), nadie se dio cuenta del peligro que el numero 27 conllevaba hasta la muerte de Kurt Cobain varias decadas despues, tambien a los 27 anos. Se inicio aqui el llamado "Club de los 27", al que tristemente se sumaria la cantante Amy Winehouse en 2011.

programme.title: MUERTE EN ALTO CONTRASTE
programme.desc: Gabriel, agente de un grupo policial tactico, ha decidido tomarse la justicia en sus propias manos para vengar la muerte de sus padres.

programme.title: Circuito Argentina
programme.desc: Argentina, sus paisajes y su gente nos esperan en este viaje fantastico con la compania del Chino Darin

When Bhambal loses his job, her working is essential; he loses self respect, and the gulf between them widens. Arati questions whether to keep her daughter in school. At work, her friendship with Edith, a Euro-Indian who smokes, swears, and uses lipstick, brings Arati close to impertinence with her genial boss. Her job is imperiled, she acts impulsively, and who will understand her actions?

programme.desc: We reach Dubai where we will crown the new champion for SCL 2016. This is part one of the world finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 15, Dubai World grand finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: We reach Dubai where we will crown the new champion for SCL 2016. This is part one of the world finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: We are in beautiful Norway for the kick off of the 2017 MLO Strongman Champions League season. With partly cloudy weather and lots of snow, we have the perfect scenery for the athletes, who prepare for the first contest of the year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: A definite highlight in this FIBO edition in Germany, Strongman Champions League introduced its new rules for a special team item. Graham Hicks tries here to set a New World Record on the biggest log in the world, currently held by Krzysztof Radzikowski. Boosted also by the presence of the acclaimed in the strongman circles names of Mark Felix and Danis Zageris.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: This weekend sees the Strongman Champions League Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. Big lifting names such as Graham Hicks , Vidas Blekaitis and Vytatus Lalas are in the startlist to push some big numbers.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: The battle of the Dutch will take place this edition in Lichtenvoorde, a place very well known in Holland because of the famous “Black Cross”. The athletes will compete over six heavy events and the winner gets 25 Strongman Champions League ranking points.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Set in the beautiful mountain resort Zlatibor, the fifth stage of the Strongman Champions League 2017 sees 14 athletes from across the world competing for the gold medal of SCL Serbia 2017. The event welcomes top-athlete - and odds-on favourite - Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia), who has presented himself in an impressive shape so far. Can his opponents defeat him?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: The next two stages take place in Quebec. With eight events over two days, SCL Canada is a true ‘heavyweight’. The athletes compete in: Truck Pull, Deadlift with cars, Log Lift, and the Atlas Stones. The World’s Strongest Viking Jean-Francois Caron from Canada is a favourite, as well as current SCL leader Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and promising underdog Jimmy Paquet (Canada).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Welcome to the second day in Quebec. The athletes are fighting hard to win this two-day event. The last points of this SCL stage can be won over four outstanding disciplines: Power Stairs, Dumbbell Press, Keg Toss, and finally, the legendary Farmer’s Walk. Who will leave Canada with the yellow ‘Leader Shirt’?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Stages 8 and 9 of the SCL are hosted in Vaasa, Finland, taking place over a spectacular two-day event. After 3 wins so far, Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia plans to extend his lead at the top of the table. Among the other 13 highly motivated strongmen, two SCL legends will make their comeback to the competition: Former World Champion of 2015, Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland) and Dainis Zageris (Latvia).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: The fight for the Finnish trophy continues. In this unmissable SCL event, the strongmen battle for the win in the Carry and Drag, the Forward Hold, Deadlifting with Cars and the Loading Race. Belsak, Radzikowski and Zageris look good after the first day, but the others haven’t given up yet.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 10, Finland Lightweight World Championship
programme.desc: This under 105kg category event is the ultimate preparation for up-and-coming strongman athletes before entering the heavy class. The Lightweight World Championship is a special every year in the SCL calendar as it sees new talents rise and many promising athletes who are gearing up for future tournaments. A total of 25 athletes from 16 different countries make their way to Kokkola, Finland

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 15, Mexico World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first day of the two-part finale sees the strongest men competing in Carry and Drag, Dumbbell Lift and the Truck Pull. Everything is possible in this heated fight for the crown against the backdrop of stunning Chetumal, Mexico.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: On the second day of the grand finale of the 2017 Strongman Champions League, the athletes have a last chance to secure the medals in the spectacular four events Weight for Height, Deadlift Cars, Forward Hold and The Loading Medley. Be prepared for stunning performances – and even world records!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Jim Clark's Top 10 Greatest Drives
programme.desc: 52 years ago on the 7th of April 1968, F1 lost it's benchmark driver Jim Clark. To celebrate his sporting achievements, we've taken a look through his races and picked out his top 10 drives, along with some help from the man himself.

programme.title: Motorsport Heroes
programme.desc: Motorsport Heroes' tells the story of five legends of motorsport, whose lives are intimately intertwined and interconnected as they all scale the heights of their sport, while contending with profound personal challenges along the way. Featuring Mika Hakkinen, Tom Kristensen, Michele Mouton and Felipe Massa, the 111-minute feature film written by Manish Pandey allows four of the greatest warriors of the sport to reflect on their lives, bringing out of each other the story of those transformations and their tales of the best and worst of times. It is also the story of the man who connects them, Michael Schumacher, viewed as the greatest winner of them all but whose story, like the others, is filled with the same fallibility and emotion that makes him human.

programme.title: Massa's F1 Legal Challenge Analysis: Aiming to "Bring The Trophy Home"
programme.sub-title: Massa's F1 Legal Challenge Analysis: Aiming to "Bring The Trophy Home"
programme.desc: Felipe Massa and his legal team have begun a legal process against the FIA & FOM regarding the 2008 F1 season, in which they believe the response to the 2008 Singapore GP Crashgate scandal was not dealt with properly – leading to Massa losing the title to Lewis Hamilton by just one point. We've spoken to a key lawyer in Massa's case, Bernardo Viana, to find out more, as Jon Noble and Alex Kalinauckas analyse the legal case and discuss the wider impact it may have on the future of F1.

programme.title: WEC
programme.sub-title: Aston Martin's Hypercar: Back in Top Class Endurance Racing
programme.desc: It's true - Aston Martin is officially set to race in WEC & IMSA with its Hypercar Prototype, based on the Aston Martin Valkyrie AMR Pro race car, with The Hearts of Racing team. But with their recent successes in F1, will they be fighting for wins and championships in Endurance Racing? What are the tech specifics about their machinery? And who will drive for the team? Martyn Lee chats with Autosport's Sportscar guru Gary Watkins to find out all the info.

programme.title: Motorsport Heroes
programme.desc: Motorsport Heroes' tells the story of five legends of motorsport, whose lives are intimately intertwined and interconnected as they all scale the heights of their sport, while contending with profound personal challenges along the way. Featuring Mika Hakkinen, Tom Kristensen, Michele Mouton and Felipe Massa, the 111-minute feature film written by Manish Pandey allows four of the greatest warriors of the sport to reflect on their lives, bringing out of each other the story of those transformations and their tales of the best and worst of times. It is also the story of the man who connects them, Michael Schumacher, viewed as the greatest winner of them all but whose story, like the others, is filled with the same fallibility and emotion that makes him human.

programme.desc: Stealing Rodin tells the unforgettable story of the greatest art theft in Chile's history. In 2005, the Palace of Fine Arts in Santiago, hosted a collection by celebrated French sculptor Auguste Rodin. The morning after the exhibit’s opening, museum guards were dismayed to find that one of the Rodin pieces had gone missing. The "theft" turned out to be a provocative statement, masterminded by a precocious art student. His actions sparked a public outcry and a furious debate on the nature of art itself.

programme.title: Dreamcars

programme.title: 4x4
programme.desc: El Defender es uno de los todoterrenos más antiguos. Puede ser ruidoso e incómodo, pero es totalmente genuino en su simplicidad. Echamos un vistazo a la historia de Land Rover. También: El Range Rover Evoque en la legendaria Ruta de la Seda.

programme.title: Dreamcars

programme.title: Supercoches

El F-Type no solo tiene buena pinta, sino que tiene lo que hace falta, y el coche es capaz de enfrentarse a la competencia como el BMW Z4. Y ademas, echamos un vistazo a otros dos competidores: el Porsche Boxster S y el 370 Z de Nissan.

programme.title: Jochen Mass en el Mercedes flecha de plata W125

programme.desc: In 1960s Paris, bourbon and money flowed freely in the neighborhood of Pigalle. Here, the city came alive at night behind closed curtains and in the company of gender-bending performers and prostitutes who made love without boundaries. Then there was Georgia - alias Gigola - a temptress who dressed like a refined young man and used her charm and wits to rise to the top of the urban underworld.

programme.desc: Three lifelong friends involved in a love triangle embark on a road trip that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: Ma Cherie TV Season 2 Episode 2
programme.desc: In this first episode of season number 12, Cherie Laurent continues with the 5th episode of Don & Cherie. The show opens with a conversation from an earlier episode of Ma Cherie called Life and Beyond. In this episode, Don & Cherie will discuss our journey of life—in particular, about the journey of one women’s life named Emily. We will travel through time of Emily’s life and as we observe Emily’s journey we may ask: what does the word time mean to you? How do you spend your time, and are you satisfied with the time that has passed thus far in your life? Do you ever wish that you could go back in time, or fast forward time? As we watch this episode, Don & Cherie helps us to reflect on our own life and it helps us think how time is a precious gift that should not be wasted.

programme.title: Hold Your Peace
programme.desc: When the hopelessly single Aiden is asked to be the best man at his ex-boyfriend Max's commitment ceremony, he finds himself confronting unresolved heartache. Rather than go alone, Max invites his roommate's outrageous friend Lance to pose as his boyfriend. But, in the days leading up to the ceremony, Aiden discovers the awkward tension may be more than he can handle.

programme.title: Exit
programme.desc: Samir is 19 years old and from South Sudan. He reached Hamburg two years ago. Last winter, falling - temperatures forced him into prostitution.

programme.title: Family Life
programme.desc: The 25 year old daughter has moved back home to her aging parents. We get to follow the family - members in their sexual dreams, their attempts to family solidarity and in vulnerable health. A - queer family picture of a seemingly straight family.

With both Brad and his wife Marcia seeking solace in destructive ways, their lives and relationships are pushed to the brink, culminating in tragic confrontations that no one can avoid. Starring Broadway Star Anthony Rapp (Rent).

programme.title: Elvis and Madonna
programme.desc: In Copacabana, lesbian photographer Elvis is hired to deliver pizzas in the night shift on her motorcycle. Her first assignment is a delivery to the transvestite hairdresser Lady Madonna. Before long, the two fall in love and move in together. But the past may come back to haunt them...

programme.title: Fair Haven

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: GLORY 85 will feature the four-man heavyweight tournament featuring two-time tournament finalist Jahfarr Wilnis (33-13-1, 8 KO), Heavyweight newcomer Murat Aygun (33-3-0), Nigerian giant Tariq ‘Cookie’ Osaro (22-2-1), and ‘The Iron Bull’ Enver Sljivar (40-6, 23 KO). A kickboxing legend will also make his return on April 29 as former two-time GLORY champion Murthel Groenhart (69-25-3, 40 KO) challenges current welterweight champion Endy Semeleer (33-1, 17 KO) for the title.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: In the main event, featherweight champ Petch (168-39-3, 27 KO) looks to defend his crown for the sixth time when he welcomes the challenge of local hero Ahmad Chikh Mousa (58-8-1, 28 KO). The co-main event will see a crucial fight between Romania’s Benjamin Adegbuyi (35-8, 20 KO) and Sofian Laïdouni (35-2-1, 17 KO) of France that will decide who will qualify for the GLORY Heavyweight Grand Prix in December.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: The interim-GLORY Heavyweight Title will be up for grabs as top ranked heavyweight contender Antonio Plazibat (22-4, 16 KO) collides with the number two ranked Tariq ‘Cookie’ Osaro (24-2-1, 12 KO) in the main event. These teammates will have to put their friendship aside for one night and go head-to-head for GLORY gold. Also on the card are title fights in the Middleweight, Welterweight and Light Heavyweight divisions.

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: A four-man one-night heavyweight tournament will take centre stage with the winner punching his ticket into the historic end of year GLORY Heavyweight Grand Prix for a chance to win a life-changing $500,000. The four participants are Dutch giant Martin Terpstra (21-5, 11 KO), former light heavyweight title contender Mohamed Amine (29-5, 16 KO), the explosive Bahram Rajabzadeh (62-1, 56 KO), and the bruising power puncher Uku Jürjendal (18-7, 14 KO). A huge international title fight will feature in the co-main event as Tyjani Beztati (24-4, 9 KO) will put his GLORY lightweight championship on the line against Japanese star Kaito Ono (51-6-1, 22 KO).

programme.title: GLORY Kickboxing
programme.desc: A huge title fight rematch will take place in the main event as rivals Tiffany ‘Time Bomb’ van Soest (24-6-2, 9 KO) and Sarah Moussaddak (8-3, 1 KO) lock horns once again. The rest of the card is stacked with some exciting names and thrilling fights. French Algerian Nordine Mahieddine (27-15, 12 KO) collides with France’s Abderahmane Coulibaly (58-20-1, 25 KO) in a big heavyweight contest, Germany’s Denis Wosik (37-8-1, 9 KO) meets the super popular Albanian Berjan Peposhi (27-3, 16 KO), former GLORY title challenger Karim Ghajji (103-17-1, 53 KO) returns and squares-off against Serbia’s Nikola Todorovic (26-3, 14 KO), and Iliass Hammouche (32-6, 7 KO) will finally make his much anticipated debut against Germany’s Florian Kroger (19-9, 6 KO).

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: The Helping Board & The Balloon Burst
programme.desc: Bramble worries people might get tripped by the fallen branches after the rain, so he tries to clear the branches on the road. Warren and Herbert offer to help. Bramble goes to dump the branches. Sheriff Chinchilla see Herbert and Warren, and takes a picture of them. The picture is posted on the Helper Board in the kindergarten the next day. Bramble feels sad that he isn’t in the picture. Sheriff happens to come to the kindergarten to take some pictures, so Bramble follows her around. He hopes the sheriff can take a picture of him doing some good deeds. But Bramble causes only trouble instead. He sees Violet who’s sweeping the fallen leaves, and realizes it doesn’t matter whether to get praised or not.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: Where is Tiki? & The Gift of Joy
programme.desc: Vick teaches Tiki how to ride a bike. Tiki wants more practice and borrows Vick’s bike. He promises to return it before noon. However, Vick still doesn’t get his bike back when noon passes and is worried that Tiki might fall from the bike. On his way to find Tiki, Vick learns from his friends that Tiki takes Luna-Loo and Violet for a ride. Vick doesn’t feel happy about that. He finds out his bike is broken when he finally finds Tiki. The two friends have a quarrel. Luna-Loo and Violet come and explain that Tiki was just trying to help them. Tiki and Vick apologize to each other. They all help Vick fix his bike.

programme.title: Boonie Cubs
programme.desc: The cubs break the trophy they won at the sports meeting. Fear of being criticized by Ms. Oliva, they make up a story that a blue bird attacks Briar and accidentally breaks the trophy. Ms. Olivia sees through their lie and gives them a lesson on honesty. The cubs confess their fault, and fix the trophy together.

programme.title: Boonie Cubs
programme.desc: Bramble decides to keep the caterpillar he finds on his head, and see how it grows up and becomes a butterfly. As time goes by, the caterpillar becomes a pupa, and soon it will turn into a butterfly. But in the process of metamorphosis, Bramble worries that it might get stuck, and tries to help. Ms. Olivia stops him and tells him that it needs to do it itself to get enough strength to fly. Just as they expected, the butterfly finally comes out, dries its wings, and flies.

programme.title: Boonie Cubs
programme.desc: The kids at Pine Tree Kindergarten are discussing what they want to be when they grow up. Vick says he wants to be an inventor and boasts that it’s easy to invent. To prove his point, he wants to invent something to dig holes as well as something for him to fly. However, both inventions meet with failure. Just when he is discouraged, he sees little Briar and Tiki playing paper planes. They are having a little contest. Then Vick gets an idea when he sees Bramble’s balloon. He attaches the balloon to the paper plane, and invents a “balloon plane” which could fly the most distance.

programme.title: Boonie Cubs
programme.desc: The cubs have got a new classmate – Ernie Jo, whose ears look different. A rumor starts that Ernie Jo’s big ears are infectious. Everybody tries to avoid him until Babu touches one of his ear by accident and he’s totally fine. The rumor is cleared and the cubs accept him. They invite Ernie Jo to play hide and seek. With the help of his big ears, Ernie Jo leads the cubs to find Little Vick who has fallen asleep and snores during the game. Now everybody wishes to have big ears like Ernie Jo’s do.

programme.title: Boonie Cubs
programme.sub-title: Rainy Day Fun & The More, The Better?
programme.desc: Violet hates rainy days. She doesn’t get why the others are having fun as usual. She tries to practice her flute, but rain drops cause her flute to get out of tune. Violet gets quite embarrassed and bursts into tears. To comfort her, everybody else gets busy doing funny tricks. Violet stops crying, asks why they enjoy the rain, and finds her own fun on rainy days.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: Velvet Touch the rabbit and her senior fellow apprentice Trapper are performing acrobatics on the stage. Velvet Touch does not perform actions according to plan and muffs the performance. In the end the stage is even destroyed. In the evening, Velvet Touch’s master calls her over. He says that he plans to establish a chain acrobatics troupe and asks her to serve as leader. Velvet Touch feels very happy but Trapper knows that the master just makes an excuse to turn her away. Trapper is worried about Velvet Touch and decides to stay with her. The next morning, Velvet Touch gets up and finds that all the people have gone except Trapper. She is very sad and realizes that her master has abandoned her. Trapper consoles him and promises to assist her in the future days.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: Velvet Touch and Trapper stop at Carrotown for a rest. At night, Trapper transforms himself into Mad Wolf. He goes to plough twelve thousand square meters of field and digs out lots of treasures, which help villagers get over the great drought. Velvet Touch hears about Mad Wolf’s chivalric story and admires him a lot. Just then, she sees Trapper sleeping outside the house covered with mud and starts complaining about him.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The annual dragon boat race is cancelled due to the upcoming flood but the dragon boats are still on the river. Most villagers go to reap the harvest and only a few people are trying to pull the boats onto the bank. The tea shop owner Mr. Ferret is very anxious and says that villagers will inevitably suffer great losses once the flood pours in and destroys the boats. After hearing the news, Trapper transforms himself into Mad Wolf again in the evening and begins to pull the boats ashore one by one.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: Two watchmen tell the Kitchen God that Mad Wolf is well qualified to be a sacred animal, and then the Kitchen God flies to Carrotown to look for him. He comes across with many people but cannot find the right one. He walks into a teahouse and sees Trapper putting on a variety show. He talks to Trapper for a while and rules out the possibility of his being the right person he needs.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: It's all Because of the Lollipop
programme.desc: Joe Croaker finds himself a treat of a large lollipop. After gorging on it, Joe places the hollowed lollipop around his neck and starts to toy with it. Not until he tries in vain to remove the lolly does he realize that he is stuck in it. As the lolly around Joe’s neck begins to melt, it becomes sticky and attracts many leaves to it. Joe looks just like a scary monster in that leafy lollipop! The other bug buddies are all frightened at the sight of Joe, mistaking him for the ruthless monster that has swallowed Joe alive. To revenge their good friend, the folks conceive a plan to capture “the monster”. Joe is cornered into a big ditch, where the lollipop around his neck is broken apart by McBroom’s dung ball. Not until then do the folks realize that the “monster” is none other than Joe Croaker! Just when the frog is about to fly off the handle, his buddies have already made themselves scarce.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is intrigued when he sees Niddy travels with her silk. The frog believes he might be able to do the same.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: Joe's got a Fish Bone in His Throat
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is on the prowl for food and the fish obtained by Cosmo makes his mouth water. As is typical of Joe Croaker the greedy bully frog, he snatches the fish from Cosmo and quickly swallows it whole. But such voracity only results in the bones being stuck in Joe’s throat. Seeing Joe in great pain, Cosmo is in panic and at a loss what to do to help. At that moment, Bartle Bee happens to pass by and offers Joe his nectar to help ease the pain. But it fails to work. Then Bartle suggests two possible solutions he learnt from books, which are ramming down the bones with a bun and dissolving them with vinegar. Cosmo and Joe hurry to the Garbage can and score both a bun and a bottle of vinegar, but it turns out neither way helps remove the bones from Joe’s throat. In the end, proposed again by the resourceful Bartle Bee, they hang Joe Croaker upside down and succeed in swinging the bones out of Joe’s throat.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Fed up living in his shabby can house, Cosmo decides to find himself a sleek, cozy new place. First he is taken with the fancy-looking paper box with pretty patterns and good light, but Bartle Bee reminds him of its vulnerability to rain in wet seasons. So he keeps on searching his dream home. Then, a crystal clear glass jar commands Cosmo’s attention. Just when he is about to make it his new abode, the mole cricket’s warning against this heat-accumulating material discourages him from settling down there. So Cosmo has to look for other alternatives. Then he discovers a large magnet which he uses to attract pieces of parts together and make them into a solidly constructed iron house. After a long day’s rushing about, Cosmo retires to rest at his pleasant new home. But something bad happens. A coin is drawn to the magnet house and blocks the exit. Trapped inside his own house, Cosmo shouts for help, which invites Joe Croaker over. The frog agrees to help him out on the condition that Cosmo offers him both service and food. But instead of getting Cosmo out, Joe accidentally sets a large iron lid running, which crashes into the magnet house. Luckily enough, Cosmo is able to survive with the help of the mole cricket. In the end, Joe Croaker has to compensate Cosmo by offering him his service instead.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo has got a nice ice cream postage stamp, which is overheard by Joe Croaker. The thought of the tasty ice cream tempts the amphibian into a plot to steal the stamp from Cosmo. He tails Cosmo, and tries in vain to grab the stamp. Tired from the flight, Cosmo rests himself upon a branch, covering himself with the stamp. Seeing this as a good opportunity, Joe employs every possible method known to him to try to score the stamp. But none of them really works. Then the green vines hanging down the tree inspire him. He uses the vines to climb up and reaches out for the stamp. He then falls off onto the ground along with the stamp. Just when Joe assumes he has secured the ice cream stamp for good, a gust of wind blows it up to the tree again. Cosmo wakes up and joyfully takes the stamp back home.

Babu realizes that his father loves him in his own way.

programme.desc: Luna-Loo’s mom is going out for a trip. Her dad grows some flowers, intending to give her mom a surprise when she comes back. She sees some wild flowers can grow very well without anyone tending them, so she decides not to take care of the orchid. The flower looks withered after just a few days. Luna-Loo realizes she needs to put in effort to gain something. She starts to take good care of the lily, which begins to grow well. At last she’s able to present her beautiful flowers to her mom when she comes back.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: Ernie Jo’s Gifts & The Paper Boats
programme.desc: Ernie Jo makes a wooden vase, but only Tiki likes it. Ernie Jo is glad Tiki likes weird things just like him. So Ernie Jo gives Tiki a lot of gifts. However, Tiki doesn’t have enough room for those gifts, so he exchanges those gifts for bananas with his friends. Ernie Jo is very angry when he finds out what happens. Tiki realizes his mistake and exchange his gifts back. Ernie Jo the trouble he causes and forgives him. The cubs finally decide to share their gifts with one another.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The two watchmen land on earth and read out the royal edict to the Kitchen God. The Kitchen God takes over the edict with reverence and awe and follows them onto a mass of cloud heading for the Heaven. They look down at the village on the way and find the masses offering sacrifice to the Kitchen God, praying for happiness and good fortune.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: After travelling miles of the sacred Heaven, the Kitchen God comes to the magnificent Hall of Miraculous Mist in the Golden-gated Cloud Palace. He poses a “V” (stands for victory) gesture with Aquila in front of the palace and asks Sonar to draw a portrait of them to mark the occasion. Shortly after, a lowly clerk comes over and brings the Kitchen God into the palace.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The Jade Emperor orders Aquila and Sonar to come down to earth and assist the Kitchen God with the task. Meanwhile, Rascal the rat finds the royal edict in the Kitchen God’s house and considers it a good opportunity to change the destinies of his family and himself. Rascal hides the edict to keep other animals from seeing it while the Kitchen God sees through his ruse and tries to recapture the edict. They get into an argument and start to scramble for the edict. Just then, Aquila and Sonar break into the house and join the scramble for the royal edict immediately. In the midst of chaos, the royal edict drops into a censer and is burned into ashes.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The Kitchen God, Rascal, and the two watchmen stand helplessly in front of the censer. Suddenly, a beam of golden light comes from the hearth and the royal edict floats up to the sky. The edict is made public and the news about the upcoming guardian tournament spreads like wildfire. The Kitchen God feels very remorseful for not keeping the secret. However, Aquila says that in that case they don’t need to worry about where to look for the competitors because all the masters will gather at Mount Tai from every corner of the village at that time.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is taking a stroll around the Marsh when all of a sudden a giant “owl” falls from the sky. Fearing that the scary bird would devour him, Joe hides himself behind a big rock. Bartle Bee passes by and finds something wrong about this furious “owl”. After a close examination, he discovers that this is not a bird but a paper kite. To fly the kite, Joe slides down a slope to help the kite gain altitude. The kite soars into the sky, taking Joe along on an exciting flight. At first, the fact that he’s ten feet off the ground frightens Joe Croaker. But as he manages to keep the kite under control, he finds himself fascinated by the midair adventure. Joe flies his “glider” and snatches the cheese from Cosmo, which makes the latter really angry. Joe gets completely carried away, when the kite flies into a desert scattered with cacti and becomes out of hand. In the end, Joe crashes in a huge cactus with his “glider”.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is casting about desperately for something to fill his empty stomach. Luckily for him, he finds some biscuits in a large can. So he jumps right into the can and gobbles up all the biscuits. But after the feast, the frog finds himself unable to get out of the can with an overstuffed belly. He tries all sorts of avenues and finally manages to hop up to the top. Suddenly, the can starts to roll down a slope. Joe freaks out inside the running can and cries for help, which is heard by Cosmo and Bartle Bee who happen to play nearby. They attempt to put a stop to the crazy can, but to no avail. At last, the can is halted on the edge of a cliff. Just when the Bartle Bee and his friends think they are safe, a rock comes running down, knocking the can down into the river. Fortunately enough, the three of them are saved by a large lotus leaf.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Bartle Bee finds a flowering plant in the forest. It is so good-looking that when Bartle Bee leaves, Joe Croaker brings it home and plants it in his back yard. The frog loves the plant and does not allow anyone except himself to touch it. But Cosmo still gets a nimble off one flower petal and the fly becomes extremely aggressive. Cosmo beats Joe Croaker up and makes the frog do his chores and give him massage.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo finds a discarded solar-powered toy car in the bush. He decides to keep it as a desirable toy. He shows off his new acquisition to Joe Croaker, who is immediately taken with the car as well. Joe Croaker seizes the car from Cosmo and tries to tug it home. As noon comes, the solar-powered car harnesses enough energy from the sun and starts to run on its own. Joe Croaker ties the car to a little tree, trying to keep it still. But fully charged with solar energy, the car breaks free of the restraint and takes Joe Croaker on an exciting road trip. Though a bit scared, Joe gets off on this wild car adventure. He snatches Cosmo’s cheese on the way. The car runs wild again and plunges into a pond, drowning Joe Croaker as well. Cosmo catches up, only to find his cheese cake gone under water.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo spots a paper boat on the stream. He picks two fine leaves as paddles and begins to go around in his boat. Flutterby is interested in the boat and she asks if she can join Cosmo. Cosmo refuses and Flutterby decides to make one boat on her own. She selects a large leaf and bends it into a boat.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Briar and Tiki chases their kite to Old Billy’s vegetable patch, and accidentally trample the vegetables. Although they try to correct the deed, but it just get worse. They try to avoid Old Billy in school and hesitate to apologize to him, for fear Old Billy will be angry. Briar tries to get Tiki and apologize to Old Billy. The old man tells them he’s going to the vegetable field to grow new vegetables. Briar and Tiki help him out. At last, they tell Old Billy the truth. The old man doesn’t get angry. Instead, he thinks they are responsible kids.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Luna-Loo doesn’t want to keep her old or broken toys, and asks her parents to buy her new ones. So she secretly throws away her old toys. When she visits Violet’s home, however, she finds out her friends treasure her toys very much, and remembers the good times she has spent with her toys. Then it rains. Luna-Loo quickly goes outside to find her toys with Violet but can’t find them. She’s feels regret. The next morning, she’s surprised to find out that all her toys are back. It turns out her mom picks up those toys, cleans and mends them. Luna-Loo realizes her mistake and thanks her mom. Violet and Vick come to Luna-Loo’s home and help her modify some old toys. Everyone is happy.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: Summoning the Sun & The Frog Friends
programme.desc: Luna-Loo stays at Violet’s home for the night. They borrow a toy car from Vick powered by solar energy. However, the car runs out of power at night. They are disappointed to find out the sun has already set. They decide to summon the sun. First they to use some “magic spells”, then an ice cream to “entice” the sun to come out. They even mimic the sound of roosters to try to call for the sun. The sun never comes out. Instead, Violet’s parents are woken by the noise. Through a little experiment, they explain to the kids about solar rotation and the switch of night and day.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Briar and Bramble discover that Old Billy’s office smells bad. They decide to help him get rid of the awful smell. They try to collect some fresh clean air from a flower field with bottles, and bring the air to the office. However, it’s hard to tell whether the fragrance is really inside the bottles. So they decide to use balloons to collect the scent. However, a little hedgehog accidentally pops the balloons when he tries to help them. Old Billy sees them and tells them that the stinky smell will go away if they keep good ventilation in the office.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is frightened upon spying what he believes to be a monster strolling around the pond. He soon realizes that the “monster” is actually a duck, but can’t work out that it’s in fact a toy duck. Assuming that this Rubber Ducky of Death is scheming to occupy his place, Joe Croaker flips out and decides to teach it a good lesson. He bullies the Rubber Ducky of Death until Bartle Bee sweeps it away. Bartle Bee is determined to rescue what he too, sadly, sees as a real—if unresponsive—duck. Joe gives chase to the two runaways, and they tangle with each other. During the confrontation, Bartle Bee accidentally gives the air-filled toy duck a prick with his sting, causing it to deflate and fly away. Still in the dark, Bartle Bee blames the disappearance of the poor little “creature” on Joe Croaker.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker finds a balloon dinosaur among the grass. The frog has no idea what he has discovered and he really panics at this “dinosaur” that is many times his own size. Joe Croaker begins to attack the balloon with pebbles he picks up from the ground. One of the pebbles bounces off the balloon and hits Bartle Bee’s honey jar on the ground. Though Joe Croaker tells Bartle Bee that he has nothing to do with the broken honey jar, the bee is smart enough to figure it out by himself.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo eats up all the food Joe Croaker has obtained, which puts the latter into a violate passion. And his mockery about Joe Croaker’s inability to fly adds fuel to fire. The hot-air balloons floating in the sky inspire the frog, who then manages to put together one with all the parts he collects from the garbage can. Flying with the ill-made balloon, Joe Croaker grabs the food from Cosmo and endeavors to catch the fly. But the balloon is too slow for Cosmo, so Joe plays dead to bamboozle Cosmo, who falls for it and ends up being caught. Just at that moment, the candle in the balloon exhausts itself. Both Joe Croaker and Cosmo fall to the ground, where the frog resumes his chase after his little foe.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker comes across a roly-poly toy when he is trying to get some candy near a dumpster. It’s a big smiling face doll. But the frog has no knowledge of what he is facing. He sees the roly-poly as a potential threat to him and the Marsh. Joe Croaker challenges the toy and attempts to take it down. The frog fails and finally he uses a rope to tie the roly-poly toy up.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: As the dung balls keep piling up, McBroom finds himself short of energy to get his work done all by himself. At Bartle Bee’s suggestion, he puts up a recruitment ad to look for someone to help him. The handsome benefits offered on this job allure many insects over, including Hercules Beetle, Snout Beetle and Bartle Bee. To select the best out of the three candidates, McBroom put them on a series of tests where Hercules Beetle stands out to win the position as McBroom’s assistant. Much to McBroom’s disappointment, however, his employee turns out to be quite lazy. So he has to give Hercules Beetle the sack and send him home.

programme.sub-title: It's all Because of the Lollipop

programme.title: Moconomy - Economía y Finanzas
programme.desc: Moconomy muestra documentales sobre negocios y finanzas.

programme.title: Grjngo - Películas Del Oeste
programme.desc: Grjngo es la fuente de streaming más grande del mundo para las películas del oeste.

programme.title: What's In the Barn?
programme.desc: “A Motorcycle Crime Story”: The horrific tale of a double murder over money and motorcycles.

programme.title: What's In the Barn?
programme.desc: “Yes, Dale there is a 100 Year Old Harley”: Dale hopes his labor of love becomes a prized possession when a six-figure Harley goes to auction.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: Post-World War II, a large generation of American soldiers was looking for cars that mirrored the incredible sports cars they saw overseas in Europe. After searching for an affordable way to recreate these cars, one manufacturer responded with a durable, cost effective option: a line of fiberglass sports cars. Very few of these cars still exist but there are collectors who are constantly looking to save parts and pieces of these virtually unknown vehicles. We learn about these rare cars from Geoff Hacker and his team at Forgotten Fiberglass, and take a visit to the Smithsonian Museum, which houses a fiberglass car of its own. This episode presents a unique look at how the narrative of American wartime experiences often shaped the nation’s automotive demands.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: Ray explores buying a unique, hand built car the Schultz family has kept in their New Jersey home for years. The car was originally called the Schultz El Fierro but it’s officially titled in New Jersey as a “Schultz Special” from 1958. It was used to drag race and held numerous racing records, but most important to the family was that it was driven by the legendary Carroll Shelby. With a frame and style much similar to the Shelby Roadster, the Schultz family wonders if it inspired one of the most well known automobiles in America. In another epic New Jersey story, Ray finds Mario Andretti’s 1965 IndyCar. The catch: it’s completely in pieces hidden away in a garage. The iconic driver talks about his days on the track with that car and Ray attempts to negotiate a deal to buy the parts.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: How do you cast a car in a movie? What are the secrets to the build? We also hear the backstory to “Bumble Bee” from Transformers, take a look at the making of the tanks for Hunger Games and stumble upon the iconic 1958 Chevy Impala from American Graffiti.

programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: While visiting the estate of automotive genius and land speed record holder Willie Glass, Ray uncovers a set of extremely rare Ardun cylinder heads, which is a hot rodders dream discovery. programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: A massive sinkhole opened underneath the National Corvette Museum in Kentucky. Eight amazing cars were swallowed up, including the 1,000,000th Corvette. programme.title: AmeriCarna
programme.desc: On the beaches of Wildwood, NJ, an iconic vintage race, The Race of Gentleman, takes place annually: period cars, period dress, pure authenticity. Ray puts a car in the race with a very special driver, who turns out not to be a Gentleman.

programme.title: AmeriCarna

programme.title: Caffeine & Octane
